Scen-Connect.sf.net >>Scenario connectors show scenarios as networks of situation and event tag pools, for fast comparisons.  It links scenarios to tags, scores, markets, chats, geotags, arphids..., creating a place that is sortable, filterable, sharable, social, and vibrant.

